🐇 4. RABBITMQ FEDERATION (CRITICAL PART)

Goal:
	•	Sync ON-PREM → AWS queues

⸻

🔹 Enable Federation Plugin

On ON-PREM RabbitMQ:

rabbitmq-plugins enable rabbitmq_federation
rabbitmq-plugins enable rabbitmq_federation_management


⸻

🔹 Configure Upstream (AWS MQ)

{
  "uri": "amqps://user:pass@aws-mq-endpoint",
  "ack-mode": "on-confirm",
  "prefetch-count": 1000
}


⸻

🔹 Policy

rabbitmqctl set_policy federation-all "^" \
'{"federation-upstream-set":"all"}' --apply-to queues


⸻

✅ Result:
	•	Messages replicated to AWS
	•	No producer change initially

